{"tid":908140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩見到個阿伯老而不廢 好撚感鳩動","createTime":"2018-11-19T11:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T12:31:02.000Z","uid":134589,"like":93,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7514770813293d55c1454cf679fdb50bb13a23dd","tid":908140,"uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭火車 坐滿人<br />\n見到個阿伯 妹下妹下咁行過黎<br />\n我左右望下見冇人讓<br />\n諗住佢會準備批鬥啲後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n突然有個巴打起左身想比佢坐<br />\n<br />\n點知佢講左句<br />\n&quot;哎返工攰呀 你坐啦 我啲幾廿歲冇野做 企下仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &quot;<br />\n嘩屌個下真係感鳩動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然呢個世界仲有啲咁撚通氣既老人家"},{"pid":"3cbc58d8b3e1b316e5bf1c3baef0f8cecbb18b8f","tid":908140,"uid":134589,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:24:44.000Z","msg":"老人家好應該要咁樣諗 唔郁動下訓練下啲肌肉<br />\n第時未一跌就散囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ee0d05ccc7ea31a800e80b2ad413caaf3a9b62","tid":908140,"uid":146535,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"一樣米都出百樣人<br />\n何況有啲食蝨米大冇晒理性<br />\n呢個阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc5097fba8f5afddc5babd1c4293c718fd39a07","tid":908140,"uid":111571,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06149d4bac7ae96e20b56b5d15fc15be5f526c93","tid":908140,"uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6bc5097fba8f5afddc5babd1c4293c718fd39a07","tid":908140,"uid":111571,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3cbc58d8b3e1b316e5bf1c3baef0f8cecbb18b8f","tid":908140,"uid":134589,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:24:44.000Z","msg":"老人家好應該要咁樣諗 唔郁動下訓練下啲肌肉<br />\n第時未一跌就散囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla